::Aerotaur::
       "Ah, my friend, it is good to see you."  He sighs.  "I'm thinking 
about heading out on my own for a while.  This team life is just too slow for 
me.  Besides it's too confining in here, I need the open spaces."  He walks 
past his friend toward the door but before leaving glances over his shoulder. 
 "If you ever need me, you'll know where to find me."  Without another word 
he walks outside and takes flight heading away from the Maximal base.

--part1_b7.2d7502aa.2b64bd8d_boundary
